<p>The <a href="https://www.apaonline.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">American Philosophical Association</a> (APA) has announced the results of its recent election.<span id="more-54051"></span></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54052 aligncenter" src="https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/apa-flag.png" alt="" width="400" height="300" srcset="https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/apa-flag.png 400w, https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/apa-flag-300x225.png 300w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /></p>
