<h3>Bylaws Amendments</h3>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;">At its meeting in November 2024, the APA board proposed coordinated <a href="https://www.apaonline.org/page/amendments2024">amendments to the association bylaws and the three sets of divisional bylaws</a>. The proposed amendments were approved by a majority of those voting in each of the divisions and have been adopted.</p>
<h3>Graduate Student Council</h3>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;"><strong>Asher Caplan</strong> (University of Oregon), 2025–2027<br />
<strong>Anton Dolmatov</strong> (Rice University), 2025–2027</p>
